1
00:00:01,036 --> 00:00:02,876
I didn't hear that, either.

2
00:00:06,139 --> 00:00:07,140
It's Tiamat!

3
00:00:09,340 --> 00:00:13,760
You have invaded the dragon's graveyard!

4
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:16,200
Wait, Tiamat!

5
00:00:16,379 --> 00:00:17,760
You have to help us!

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:22,000
What?

7
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:27,180
Way to go, Hank!

8
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:28,740
That really calmed her down!

9
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:30,760
Maybe this will make you listen!

10
00:00:30,761 --> 00:00:32,800
Huh?!

